    note right of Unbound
        Created via no-arg constructor or ServerSocket(SocketImpl).
        bind() must be called before accept().
        bind() throws IOException if already bound.
        setReceiveBufferSize() should be called before bind()
        for TCP receive windows larger than 64K.
        setPerformancePreferences() has no effect after bind().
    end note

    note right of Bound
        Bound to a local address and port.
        accept() blocks waiting for incoming connections.
        bind() throws IOException (already bound).
    end note

    note right of Closed
        Terminal state. close() is idempotent.
        setOption()/getOption() throw IOException if called on closed socket.
        setReuseAddress() throws SocketException if socket is closed.
    end note
